        "question_adqrYK": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do I properly apply the capsule cream?",
            "answer": "<p>For the best results, use the provided spatula to scoop out one or two capsules along with the surrounding gel. Mix them together in your palm or apply directly to your face, gently \"popping\" the capsules as you massage the product into your skin until fully absorbed.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_TDP7NK": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Is this product suitable for sensitive skin?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, the formula is designed to be gentle enough for daily use, both day and night. It contains soothing ingredients that help calm irritation while refining your skin's texture and tone.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_hPGXCN": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How long will it take to see results in my skin tone?",
            "answer": "<p>While many users notice an instant \"glass-skin\" glow and increased hydration immediately, significant improvements in fading dark spots and hyperpigmentation typically appear after consistent use over several weeks.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_7Rxwez": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What are the main benefits of using 5% Niacinamide and TXA together?",
            "answer": "<p>This powerful combination targets skin clarity from two angles: Tranexamic Acid (TXA) helps improve uneven skin tone and fading blemishes, while 5% Niacinamide revives dullness and smooths skin texture for a refreshed look.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_Pzgd7t": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What makes the TXA Niacinamide Capsule Cream different from regular moisturizers?",
            "answer": "<p>Unlike traditional creams, this formula features a unique capsule-in-gel texture. Each capsule contains high-purity ingredients that are freshly released upon application to ensure maximum potency and targeted results for your skin.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
